Dialogs.Dialog: You feel like you've done your research on date spots？
Have you been watching Rinko for a while now？
I'm a little sleepy... but I guess that's always the case.
I'm looking forward to my boyfriend escorting me.
Don't get too excited, you'll get tired.
It's time to take some action.
See, it's not fuzzy. You don't have to look at Rinko.
Maybe a little more like this.
How long are you going to keep looking at Rinko？
There's still a lot more dating to do.
What！？ Did you just see that？
Maybe I'm getting a little excited.
You're grinning. Are you having fun？
Today is... something better than usual.
Don't look too much, it makes me nervous.
Hey. Having fun？ Hehe, Rinko too.
It's just the two of us... Not physically, but mentally.
You know... do you like Rinko？ You don't have to answer.
I wonder how you and Rinko look to those around them.
Don't worry too much about other couples.
When is the season of lovers？ I feel like I hear that word all year round.
You know, there are times when I want my lover to speak clearly.
Hey. You and Rinko are like the best couple, aren't we？
Hey, can I kick you？ This is also a kind of nonsense expression.
Your hands are warm, I wonder why.
If we're lovers, you know, maybe we should be closer to each other.
Oh, the couple over there... well, I don't mind.
Hey, don't let your girlfriend tell you everything.
Could you and Rinko be a bit of an idiot-couple？ No way.
When we are together, there is no need for anything special.
...Hehe, I just saw you making a weird face！
Someone is staring at us. Well, I don't mind. We're lovers.
Sometimes it's nice to take a detour.
Isn't it exciting to go down a road you don't usually take？
It's okay to take our time.
All the weekdays are pretty much free.
Sometimes a casual date like this is nice.
Not too many people here today？ ...Don't think about anything strange.
I'd like to relax all the time, but I guess that's not going to happen.
This kind of thing is the privilege of students.
I wish we had more time to talk.
I wish I had more time, you know, for many things.
I'm so pissed off, it's a beautiful day. Just kidding.
It's so sunny... I wish it was calmer.
Nice weather. Is it thanks to Rinko's daily routine？
It's kind of cloudy. I wonder if it will clear up.
Maybe a little cloudy would be more comfortable.
Well, it's better that it's not raining.
Rain, huh... do you like rain？
Is there any song you want to listen to on a rainy day？
It's fun in the rain, isn't it？ It depends on how you feel.
I wonder if there is a cooler place.
Hmm～. The wind feels so nice.
It's easy to be comfortable in this kind of temperature.
Maybe it's the perfect season for a date.
There's a lot of people... Good grief.
You're making a lot of noise...
There are a lot of people here, so don't get lost, okay？
Hmm... well, it's better than having no one around.
Is it usually more crowded here？
There are a lot of people there.
Could this be a hidden spot？
It might be something like a private party.
You shouldn't show any openings in front of Rinko.
You know... I wouldn't complain if it was closer.
Why do you think I'm so impatient...？
You and Rinko are lovers, right？
Hey, let's kiss. What would you do if I said that？
Well, we're just getting started today.
When you have time, it's hard to decide what to do.
Maybe it's a negative thing to worry only about the clock when you're on a date.
What！？ Is it that late already...？
Are you okay with the time？
I wonder if it's already this late...
I know it's cliche, but good times pass quickly.
It's getting to be a pretty good time. Hah...
Hey, what do you want to do？
You have a great date plan, right？
Planning is important. I think you know that.
I wait for today's plan with anticipation...
Does it feel like a flawless plan today？
I guess I'm a little too relaxed. Don't you think so？
A date plan is just a plan. Be flexible.
How's it going？ Did today's date go according to plan？
What's next？ It's not a no-brainer.
You know what, have you decided what we're going to do after this？ Is there anything you're forgetting？
Today, you know, I was looking forward to it.
Hey, don't look away all the time.
Are you aware that you walk on the side of the road？
Where you go is important, but it's who you spend your time with and how you spend it that's crucial.
It's because Rinko doesn't have a wide stride. I'm willing to match yours.
Don't you want to skip or something？ ...I'm just kidding.
It kind of makes me want to sing, even though I don't sing.
What should we do on our next date...？
I better plan my next date.
Are you tired of working hard？
If we had a little more time, we could have enjoyed it more.
It's a date, you know, and you want to be in a good mood by the end of it.
I guess the date is over...
I feel like being selfish, but I don't want to bother you.
A couple we met along the way looked enviously at us.
Maybe I'll have a good dream tonight... like the continuation of our date.
How many times have we been here？
I think I might like it here a lot.
I heard this place was used as a location for a drama before...？
I think there was a spell that originated here, but I forgot it.
Maybe the atmosphere is not so bad.
I wonder if there is anything weird about this.
It is the duty of the boyfriend to escort, right？
Speaking of dates... what about us.
I wonder if this place will become a memory someday.
Whatever the place is, there's not enough time to get to know it.
Well, no matter where we are, it's never just the two of us.
Is today a good day for a date？
Looks like there's a place to sit over there.
Are we going to go in somewhere soon？
A place with a lot of greenery might be relaxing.
Good air makes you feel better, right？
When I'm outside, I tend to look for stray cats～.
I might have seen this place featured in a magazine.
I wonder if this place has looked like this before.
I think the air conditioner is working too well.
Hmm, this is a popular trend.
Don't get swept along with the rest of the crowd.
I guess this kind of thing is not so bad once in a while.
I'm sure it would resonate if I shouted it out here... I'm just kidding.
I think I can relax here.
Don't look at other tables too much.
I see, so this is the kind of place you're looking for.
You are a surprisingly strong type of person.
I imagine a man's room would be even more amazing.
I wonder how many times I will come to this room...
You know, can you come back again？
Let me know if you want something to drink.
How's that？ Surprisingly tidy, isn't it？
I think it's a room with relatively bad tastes...
If you're so nervous, even Rinko will... come on, relax！
Staring at the room is sexual harassment.
It's just the two of us...
This situation is on a higher level.
If you don't do something, you might not feel comfy.
No... Why do you say that？
I'm sure someone hears you saying all of those things.
Why are you... geez... you're an idiot.
I don't care anymore！ Like that.
Why don't you do it yourself？
...What is that, I can't believe it.
Don't worry, I can only see you.
You think so too？ I see.
Hmm, is that what you mean？
I'll pretend I didn't just hear that.
I couldn't hear you very well...？
Coincidence. Rinko was thinking the same thing.
Actions speak louder than words. Aren't they？
I'll take it as an informative opinion.
That's one way to do it.
I have to value you opinion too.
That's a bit of a stretch.
